        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .gff-section {\n    background: #ffffff;\n    padding: 60px 24px 32px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    min-height: auto;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n  .gff-inner {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    width: 100%;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 80px;\n  }\n  .gff-headline {\n    font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 88px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    line-height: 0.95;\n    letter-spacing: -0.03em;\n    color: #0a0a0a;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    margin: 0 0 24px 0;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n  .gff-body {\n    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.4vw, 18px);\n    line-height: 1.65;\n    color: #444444;\n    margin: 0 0 32px 0;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n  .gff-cta {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n    background: #0a0a0a;\n    color: #ffffff;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    padding: 18px 32px;\n    width: fit-content;\n    transition: gap 0.2s ease;\n  }\n  .gff-cta:hover { gap: 24px; }\n  .gff-video {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 480px;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    mix-blend-mode: multiply;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .gff-section { padding: 40px 24px 24px; }\n    .gff-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }\n    .gff-video { max-width: 260px; margin: 0 auto; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"gff-section\">\n  <div class=\"gff-inner\">\n    <div>\n      <h2 class=\"gff-headline\">FOCO SIN CULPA</h2>\n      <p class=\"gff-body\">Potenciá tu foco y energía limpia, sin el bagaje. No decimos que tenés que dejar la nicotina, pero es adictiva, restringe el flujo sanguíneo y no está optimizada para el rendimiento máximo. ¿Por qué conformarse con menos?</p>\n      <a href=\"/products/magma-energy-pouches\" class=\"gff-cta\">\n        COMPRAR AHORA\n        <svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\">\n          <path d=\"M3 9H15M15 9L9 3M15 9L9 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;\">\n      <video class=\"gff-video\" autoplay muted loop playsinline>\n        <source src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/0d4d3ea584cc4957b21804c750eded30.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n      </video>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
